Uses of Package
org.gephi.appearance.spi

  • Packages that use org.gephi.appearance.spi 
    Package Description
    org.gephi.appearance.api
    API for manipulating element appearance.
    org.gephi.appearance.spi
    Interfaces that define the different ways the appearance of elements can be transformed.
  • Classes in org.gephi.appearance.spi used by org.gephi.appearance.api 
    Class and Description
    Transformer
    Transformers role is to transform the appearance of elements based on user configuration.
    TransformerUI
    Defines the user interface associated with a transformer.
  • Classes in org.gephi.appearance.spi used by org.gephi.appearance.spi 
    Class and Description
    Transformer
    Transformers role is to transform the appearance of elements based on user configuration.
    TransformerCategory
    Transformer categories are associated with TransformerUI to describe what kind of transformation is performed.
